OL,3,CHotspots where home buyers will get
OL,4,Cmore ` or less ` floor space for their
OL,5,Cmoney
OL,7,FThe sum of #200 would get home buyers
OL,8,Fin Westminster the equivalent of just
OL,9,Fa quarter of a sheet of A4 paper in
OL,10,Ffloor space, while in Burnley in
OL,11,FLancashire this amount would stretch
OL,12,Fto more than two full sheets
OL,13,Ftypically, according to analysis by a
OL,14,Fproperty website.
OL,16,FZoopla carried out the analysis to
OL,17,Funderline to home buyers just how much
OL,18,Fspace they can typically expect to get
OL,19,Ffor their money in different locations.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
