OL,3,CHotspots where home buyers will get
OL,4,Cmore ` or less ` floor space for their
OL,5,Cmoney
OL,7,FBuyers in Westminster would have to
OL,8,Fpay #837 typically for floor space
OL,9,Fequivalent to one sheet of A4, or #686
OL,10,Fin Kensington and Chelsea, and #665 in
OL,11,FCamden, the website found.
OL,13,FAway from southern England, home
OL,14,Fbuyers in major cities including
OL,15,FManchester, Leeds, Sheffield,
OL,16,FLiverpool, Birmingham, Coventry,
OL,17,FWolverhampton, Newcastle and Cardiff
OL,18,Fcould buy a full sheet of A4-sized
OL,19,Ffloor space for #200.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
