OL,3,CHotspots where home buyers will get
OL,4,Cmore ` or less ` floor space for their
OL,5,Cmoney
OL,7,FAnd #200 could get buyers at least two
OL,8,Ffull sheets of A4 floor space in
OL,9,Flocations including Hull, Blackpool,
OL,10,FMiddlesbrough, Blaenau Gwent and
OL,11,FSunderland, according to the
OL,12,Fcalculations.
OL,14,FLooking at Scotland, in Edinburgh the
OL,15,Faverage A4-sized floor space costs
OL,16,F#204.
OL,18,FAnd in Yorkshire, an A4-sized floor
OL,19,Fspace in York will set buyers back
OL,20,Faround #209 typically.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
