OL,3,CHotspots where home buyers will get
OL,4,Cmore ` or less ` floor space for their
OL,5,Cmoney
OL,7,FZoopla has a tool which allows buyers
OL,8,Fto set a minimum square footage
OL,9,Falongside their price range.
OL,11,FRichard Donnell, executive director at
OL,12,FZoopla, said: "Our analysis shows that
OL,13,Fthe gap between what #200 gets you in
OL,14,FWestminster versus what it buys in the
OL,15,FNorth West is not just a number ` it
OL,16,Fis the difference between a sliver of
OL,17,Fa page and two full sheets of paper.
